    "subtitle": "Peaceful Garden Sandbox",
    "description": "FlowerSandbox is a peaceful, interactive digital garden where you can plant beautiful flowers, customize your garden layout, and relax with serene animations. Nurture your virtual sanctuary, experiment with colorful petals, and enjoy a calming, distraction-free environment designed for mindfulness and relaxation.\n\nFlowerSandbox Premium is an optional auto-renewable subscription (1 month, $1.00/month) that unlocks premium flower colors, special varieties, and a larger garden. Payment is charged to your Apple Account at confirmation of purchase. The subscription renews automatically unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Manage or cancel anytime in your Apple Account settings.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://flowersandbox.com/privacy\nTerms of Use (EULA): https://flowersandbox.com/terms",
